```java
public class LP3 
{
    public static void main(String[] args) 
    {
        int n = Integer.parseInt(args[0]);

        int power =1;

        while ( __0__ )
        {
            power = __1__;
        }

        System.out.println(power);
    }
}
```

Try to finish the code to compute the largest number which is the power of 3 that is less than or equal to a given positive integer n, and store the value to 'power'.

Example1:

```
java LP3 10
```

Output:

```
9
```

